Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.89,Love-Ru_Main,Mea,0,0,0,,Uầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.64,Love-Ru_Main,Nemesis,0,0,0,,Nào, đừng dỗi.
